# <%= projectName %>

Quarkus CLI walking skeleton scaffolded by keel — hexagonal, mediator-driven.

## Layout

```
domain/
  contract/    — Command, Handler, Mediator interfaces (the kernel)
  core/        — DefaultMediator + sample GreetCommand handler
infrastructure/
  cli/         — picocli + Quarkus, calls into the mediator
```

## Run

```sh
./gradlew :infrastructure:cli:quarkusDev
# or once built:
./gradlew :infrastructure:cli:run --args="hello --name World"
```

## Test

```sh
./gradlew test
```

## Build a native binary

```sh
./gradlew :infrastructure:cli:build -Dquarkus.package.type=native
```
